# **🏗️ Arquitectura de Base de Datos - Aplicación Nutricional Integrada**

## **🔐 Autenticación y Perfiles**

### **profiles**

```sql

sql
- id (uuid, PK) → Referencia a auth.users
- full_name (text)
- avatar_url (text)
- date_of_birth (date)
- height (integer) → cm
- weight (numeric) → kg
- Indice de masa corporal (BMI) (numeric)
- gender (text)
- activity_level (text) → sedentary, light, moderate, active, very_active
- created_at (timestamp)
- updated_at (timestamp)

```

### **user_health_profile**

```sql

sql
-- user_health_profile
- id (uuid, PK)
- user_id (uuid, FK) → profiles.id
- dietary_preferences (text[]) → vegetarian, vegan, keto, etc
- health_goals (text[]) → weight_loss, muscle_gain, maintenance
- allergies (text[])
- medical_conditions (text[])
- daily_calories_target (integer)
- daily_protein_target (numeric)
- daily_carbs_target (numeric)
- daily_fat_target (numeric)
- weight_target (numeric kg)
- cooking_lifestyle (text) → minimal_prep, batch_cooker, daily_fresh, cooking_enthusiast
- summary (text) (aqui va la ficha de usuario)
- nutritional_plan (text) (aqui va el plan nutricional)
- created_at (timestamp)
- updated_at (timestamp)

```

## **🥘 Sistema de Ingredientes y Recetas**

### **ingredients**

```sql

sql
- id (integer, PK, auto-increment)
- name (text, NOT NULL)
- default_unit (text) → grams, ml, cups, pieces
- calories_per_100g (numeric)
- protein_per_100g (numeric)
- carbs_per_100g (numeric)
- fat_per_100g (numeric)
- fiber_per_100g (numeric)
- category (text) → vegetables, fruits, proteins, grains, dairy
- created_at (timestamp)

```

### **recipes**

```sql

sql
- id (integer, PK, auto-increment)
- title (text, NOT NULL)
- description (text)
- image_url (text)
- user_id (uuid, nullable) → profiles.id (null = sistema)
- instructions (text)
- prep_time (integer) → minutos
- cook_time (integer) → minutos
- servings (integer)
- total_calories (numeric)
- total_protein (numeric)
- total_carbs (numeric)
- total_fat (numeric)
- meal_type (text) → breakfast, lunch, dinner, snack
- difficulty_level (text) → easy, medium, hard
- is_public (boolean, default: false)
- user_rating (integer) → 1-5
- health_score (integer) → 1-10
- created_at (timestamp)
- updated_at (timestamp)

```

### **recipe_ingredients**

```sql

sql
- recipe_id (integer, FK) → recipes.id
- ingredient_id (integer, FK) → ingredients.id
- quantity (numeric, NOT NULL)
- unit (text, NOT NULL)
- PRIMARY KEY (recipe_id, ingredient_id)

```

## **📅 Planificación de Comidas**

### **meal_plans**

```sql

sql
- id (uuid, PK)
- user_id (uuid, FK) → profiles.id
- week_start_date (date) → Lunes de la semana
- is_active (boolean, default: true)
- created_at (timestamp)
- updated_at (timestamp)

```

### **planned_meals**

```sql

sql
- id (uuid, PK)
- meal_plan_id (uuid, FK) → meal_plans.id
- recipe_id (integer, FK) → recipes.id
- day_of_week (integer) → 0=Lunes, 6=Domingo
- meal_type (text) → breakfast, lunch, dinner, snack
- start_time (integer) 
- servings_planned (numeric, default: 1)
- created_at (timestamp)

```

## **📝 Registro y Seguimiento (repaso)**

### **food_diary**

```sql

sql
- id (uuid, PK)
- user_id (uuid, FK) → profiles.id
- date (date, NOT NULL)
- meal_type (text) → breakfast, lunch, dinner, snack
- recipe_id (integer, nullable, FK) → recipes.id
- food_name (text) → Si no es receta
- quantity (numeric, NOT NULL)
- unit (text, NOT NULL)
- calories (numeric)
- protein (numeric)
- carbs (numeric)
- fat (numeric)
- fiber (numeric)
- notes (text)
- consumed_at (timestamp, NOT NULL) →  🆕 NUEVO Hora exacta de consumo
- location_type (text, default: 'unknown') → home, work, restaurant, gym, street, other 🆕 NUEVO Lugar de consumo
- time_since_last_meal (integer, nullable) → Minutos desde última comida (calculado) 🆕 NUEVO Tiempo entre comidas
- day_type (text) → 🆕 NUEVO weekday, weekend, holiday
- eating_context (text, nullable) → 🆕 NUEVO solo, familia, trabajo, social (inferido de ubicación/hora)
-- 🆕 FEEDBACK OCASIONAL (solo 1 de cada 5 registros)
- mood_emoji (text, nullable) → 😊, 😐, 😰, 😢, 😴, 🤗 (4-6 opciones) 🆕 NUEVO

- created_at (timestamp)

```

### **food_photo_analysis**

```sql

sql
- id (uuid, PK)
- user_id (uuid, FK) → profiles.id
- image_url (text, NOT NULL)
- ai_analysis_raw (jsonb) → Respuesta completa de IA
- detected_foods (jsonb) → Array de alimentos detectados
- estimated_calories (numeric)
- estimated_protein (numeric)
- estimated_carbs (numeric)
- estimated_fat (numeric)
- confidence_score (numeric) → 0-1
- is_verified (boolean, default: false)
- food_diary_id (uuid, nullable, FK) → Si se añade al diario
- created_at (timestamp)

```

### **daily_nutrition_summary Permite al agente acceder al estado de progreso**

```sql

sql
- id (uuid, PK)
- user_id (uuid, FK) → profiles.id
- date (date, NOT NULL)
- total_calories (numeric, default: 0)
- total_protein (numeric, default: 0)
- total_carbs (numeric, default: 0)
- total_fat (numeric, default: 0)
- total_fiber (numeric, default: 0)
- target_calories (numeric)
- target_protein (numeric)
- target_carbs (numeric)
- target_fat (numeric)
- adherence_score (numeric) → % de cumplimiento
- created_at (timestamp)
- updated_at (timestamp)
- UNIQUE(user_id, date)

```

## **🛒 Sistema de Compras e Inventario**

### **user_inventory**

```sql

sql
- id (integer, PK, auto-increment)
- user_id (uuid, FK) → profiles.id
- ingredient_id (integer, FK) → ingredients.id
- quantity (numeric, NOT NULL, default: 0)
- unit (text, NOT NULL)
- expiry_date (date, nullable)
- location (text) → fridge, pantry, freezer
- updated_at (timestamp)
- UNIQUE(user_id, ingredient_id, unit)

```

### **shopping_lists**

```sql

sql
- id (integer, PK, auto-increment)
- user_id (uuid, FK) → profiles.id
- name (text, default: 'Lista de compra')
- status (text, default: 'open') → open, closed, archived
- meal_plan_id (uuid, nullable, FK) → meal_plans.id
- total_estimated_cost (numeric, default: 0)
- created_at (timestamp)
- updated_at (timestamp)

```

### **shopping_list_items**

```sql

sql
- id (integer, PK, auto-increment)
- shopping_list_id (integer, FK) → shopping_lists.id
- ingredient_id (integer, FK) → ingredients.id
- quantity_needed (numeric, NOT NULL)
- quantity_have (numeric, default: 0) → Del inventario
- quantity_to_buy (numeric, NOT NULL) → Calculado
- unit (text, NOT NULL)
- estimated_price (numeric)
- is_purchased (boolean, default: false)
- purchased_at (timestamp, nullable)
- created_at (timestamp)

```

## **🏆 Gamificación y Streaks**

### daily_targets_tracking

```sql
sql
- id (uuid, PK)
- user_id (uuid, FK) → profiles.id
- date (date)
- targets_met (boolean, default: false) -- true si alcanzó TODOS sus targets del día
- created_at (timestamp)
- updated_at (timestamp)

```

### user_streak

```sql

- id (uuid, PK)
- user_id (uuid, FK) → profiles.id
- current_streak (integer, default: 0) -- días consecutivos alcanzando targets
- best_streak (integer, default: 0) -- mejor racha histórica
- last_target_date (date) -- última fecha que alcanzó targets
- updated_at (timestamp)

```